<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class="govuk-body">Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Congratulations on your progress towards completing the I Belong: encouraging girls into computer science programme.
  </p>
  <p class="goveuk-body">
    Now that your school has undertaken a range of activities to improve girls’ participation in computer science, consolidate your learning by engaging in professional development.
    The evidence-informed <%= link_to 'primary', course_url('CP409') %> or <%= link_to 'secondary', course_url('CP440') %>
    short courses developed by our specialists will help you reflect on what you’ve done so far and plan and explore different strategies to use inside and outside the classroom.
  </p>
  <%= link_to 'Book primary course', course_url('CP409'), class: 'govuk-button button' %><br/><br/>
  <%= link_to 'Book secondary course', course_url('CP440'), class: 'govuk-button button' %>
  <p class="govuk-body">Most importantly, by completing the programme, your school will achieve a nationally recognised certificate recognising its commitment to improving girls’ uptake of computer science.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Need more support?</strong></p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Go to your
    <%= link_to 'dashboard', i_belong_url %>
    to browse all recommended activities from the I Belong programme and explore the guidance available. 
  </p>
</div>
